{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/extras/EN-01.png?t=1727903100\" /><br>I have been creating this game since high school and have worked hard through my studies at Charles University in Prague. My aim for this year is to carry over my Ph.D. research about procedurally generated terrains into my game. My goal is to one day capture 150 years of racing in a single game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/extras/EN-02.png?t=1727903100\" /><br>Formula Evolution is a multiplayer racing game that uses similar principles as World of Tanks - with each race against 39 other players, you gain experience and credits, for which you can buy various upgrades for your vehicle or unlock newer vehicles. You start with machines of the 1900s. Can you get to the very top and ride on modern machinery?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/extras/EN-03.png?t=1727903100\" /><br>Controls are simplified enough to give you still the passion from riding but not too complex to take you hours to learn. It mainly focuses on providing players with the best enjoyment from racing fights possible. The game's core is short dynamic races with a high action density. The feeling from the ride is very reminiscent of older games, do not expect a hardcore simulator. On the other hand, it's not a mario kart racing game - there are physics, and you need to keep that in mind.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/extras/EN-04.png?t=1727903100\" /><br>- 40 formulas from 70 years of history<br>- 40 real and custom tracks<br>- 1000+ various vehicle setups<br>- 30+ vehicle patterns, each customizable<br>- 10 different biomes<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/extras/EN-05.png?t=1727903100\" /><br>You can customize your vehicle and rider as much as you want using a simple yet rich customization system. You can paint your formula with any combination of colors or use any of the available patterns and customize it!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/extras/EN-06.png?t=1727903100\" /><br>The game is based on custom cloud-saving technology. As part of that, it contains many classic MMO features like cloud save, leaderboards, daily missions, achievements, and stats! Compare yourself to other racers!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727903100","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/page.bg.jpg?t=1727903100","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727903100","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727903100","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"MMO","id":20},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"In-App Purchases","id":35},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Stats","id":15}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/extras/EN-01.png?t=1727903100\" /><br>I have been creating this game since high school and have worked hard through my studies at Charles University in Prague. My aim for this year is to carry over my Ph.D. research about procedurally generated terrains into my game. My goal is to one day capture 150 years of racing in a single game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/extras/EN-02.png?t=1727903100\" /><br>Formula Evolution is a multiplayer racing game that uses similar principles as World of Tanks - with each race against 39 other players, you gain experience and credits, for which you can buy various upgrades for your vehicle or unlock newer vehicles. You start with machines of the 1900s. Can you get to the very top and ride on modern machinery?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/extras/EN-03.png?t=1727903100\" /><br>Controls are simplified enough to give you still the passion from riding but not too complex to take you hours to learn. It mainly focuses on providing players with the best enjoyment from racing fights possible. The game's core is short dynamic races with a high action density. The feeling from the ride is very reminiscent of older games, do not expect a hardcore simulator. On the other hand, it's not a mario kart racing game - there are physics, and you need to keep that in mind.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/extras/EN-04.png?t=1727903100\" /><br>- 40 formulas from 70 years of history<br>- 40 real and custom tracks<br>- 1000+ various vehicle setups<br>- 30+ vehicle patterns, each customizable<br>- 10 different biomes<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/extras/EN-05.png?t=1727903100\" /><br>You can customize your vehicle and rider as much as you want using a simple yet rich customization system. You can paint your formula with any combination of colors or use any of the available patterns and customize it!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/extras/EN-06.png?t=1727903100\" /><br>The game is based on custom cloud-saving technology. As part of that, it contains many classic MMO features like cloud save, leaderboards, daily missions, achievements, and stats! Compare yourself to other racers!","developers":["Petr \u0160im\u016fnek"],"ext_user_account_notice":"Engine Evolution cloud (Supports Linking to Steam Account)","fullgame":{"appid":"2456080","name":"Formula Evolution 2024"},"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Massively Multiplayer","id":"29"},{"description":"Racing","id":"9"},{"description":"Sports","id":"18"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2472060/header.jpg?t=1727903100","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"name":"Formula Evolution 2024 Demo","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system</li></ul>"},"platforms":{"linux":false,"mac":false,"windows":true},"publishers":["Petr \u0160im\u016fnek"],"ratings":{"dejus":{"banned":"0","descriptors":"","rating":"l","rating_generated":"1","required_age":"0","use_age_gate":"0"},"steam_germany":{"banned":"0","descriptors":"","rating":"0","rating_generated":"1","required_age":"0","use_age_gate":"0"}},"release_date":{"coming_soon":false,"date":"27 Jun, 2023"},"required_age":0,"screenshots":[{"id":0,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/stea